trans-unit.source: This dialog is normally used by the activities <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.IfElseBranchActivity"></xref>, <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.WhileActivity"></xref>, <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.ConditionedActivityGroup"></xref>, and <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity"></xref> to edit declarative conditions.
trans-unit.target: Denne dialogboksen brukes vanligvis av aktivitetene <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.IfElseBranchActivity"> </xref>, <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.WhileActivity"> </xref>, <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.ConditionedActivityGroup"> </xref>, og <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity"> </xref> til å redigere deklarerende betingelser.

trans-unit.source: However, if you want to use conditions outside of these activities (for example, edit a condition for use outside of a workflow completely), you can use this dialog to perform the editing of the condition.
trans-unit.target: Men hvis du vil bruke betingelser utenfor disse aktivitetene (for eksempel redigere en betingelse for Bruk utenfor en arbeidsflyt fullstendig), kan du bruke denne dialogboksen til å utføre redigering av betingelsen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.Design.RuleConditionDialog"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.Design.RuleConditionDialog"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> that this condition is executed against.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> som denne betingelsen kjøres mot.

trans-unit.source: Typically it is the workflow, but it can be any valid activity.
trans-unit.target: Det er vanligvis arbeidsflyten, men det kan være en gyldig aktivitet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.Design.RuleConditionDialog"></xref> class with the specified activity type, the type provider, and the expression.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.Design.RuleConditionDialog"> </xref> klassen med den angitte aktivitet-typen, typen leverandøren og uttrykket.

trans-unit.source: The type of the object that this condition is executed against.
trans-unit.target: Typen for objektet som denne feilen er utføres.

trans-unit.source: Normally it is the workflow, but can be any valid type.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis den arbeidsflyten, men kan være en gyldig type.

trans-unit.source: An optional <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ITypeProvider"></xref> implementation that is used to determine what types are available in the condition.
trans-unit.target: En valgfri <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ITypeProvider"> </xref> implementering som brukes til å finne ut hvilke typer er tilgjengelige i betingelsen.

trans-unit.source: If one is not specified, only types in the assembly specified by `activityType` and any assemblies it references is available.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det ikke er spesifisert bare datatyper i samlingen angitt av `activityType` og alle samlinger den refererer til er tilgjengelig.

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.Design.RuleConditionDialog"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Frigir alle ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.Design.RuleConditionDialog"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>å frigjøre både administrerte og uforvaltede ressurser. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> frigi bare uforvaltede ressurser.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"></xref> as modified by the dialog box user.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"> </xref> som endres av dialogboksen for brukeren.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"></xref> as modified by the dialog box user.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"> </xref> som endres av dialogboksen for brukeren.
